      • getPlayerCount

        public int getPlayerCount()
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession
        The number of real human Players currently playing in this session.

        As the definition of "multiplayer" is rather loose - this method can be combined with GameSession.isRemoteServer() to determine if the player is playing alone or with others, locally or remotely.

        定義:

        public boolean isRemoteServer()
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession

        As the definition of "multiplayer" is rather loose - this method can be combined with GameSession.getPlayerCount() to determine if the player is playing alone or with others, locally or remotely.

      • getGameMode

        public java.lang.String getGameMode()
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession
        The name of the current game mode being played.

        This name will be in the form of "survival" or "spectator", but the precise values may change over time.

        This value only covers the current active players game mode, and not the general game mode of the session as a whole.

        定義:
        getGameMode インタフェース内 com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession
        戻り値:
        Current game mode name

        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession

        This is useful for keeping track of if the player is in the same session, or has left and joined a new one.
